				<td colspan="2"><span>I've seen somewhere (cant remember exactly where, so no point asking <img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-4.gif" border="0" alt="Tongue out" hspace="2" /> ) that the tasks ARE class tailored.  They are designed so EVERYONE can do them, whether your a bard, shaman, cleric, rogue or warrior.
<br />

